<p>A Steam client update is now available. To apply the update, click the File menu inside of Steam and then select \"Check for Steam Client Updates...\".  The specific changes include:<br/><br/><b>Steam Client</b><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Fixed rare cases of missing desktop shortcuts, Game Explorer links and uninstall entries<br/><li>Fixed a potential overlay crash in games that run ShellExecute with a very long command line<br/><li>Fixed input for Asian languages<br/></li></li></li></ul></p>
